{"tid":485834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慎入】伊朗女為變安祖蓮娜祖莉整容50次 減逾80磅網民嘲似屍新娘","createTime":"2017-12-01T09:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T11:59:55.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e338057a733a3b9062d07ea656e390ac1a988d61","tid":485834,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"整容前<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popnews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Sahar-before-undergoing-the-extreme-transformation-600x618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2FSahar-before-undergoing-the-extreme-transformation-600x618.jpg&h=0c6c8dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整容後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popnews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/02-768x385.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F02-768x385.jpg&h=507b1047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popnews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/04-768x327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F04-768x327.jpg&h=d4e1f440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊朗德黑蘭少女塔芭（Sahar Tabar）是荷里活女星安祖蓮娜祖莉（Angelina Jolie）狂熱粉絲。為了和偶像變得相像，更自稱在幾個月內進行了逾50次整容手術，更以節食的方式減去了40公斤體重，手法相當極端。整容後她不時會在個人instagram上分享自拍，然而網民對於她的樣貌似乎就不太受落更直指「恐怖」，又指她更像《怪誕屍新娘》中的屍新娘維多莉亞。從塔芭分享的照片中所見，她臉型極為瘦削，突起的顴骨和厚唇明顯仿傚了祖莉的樣貌特徵。不少網民都對塔芭的行為感到不理解，在她的instagram留下負評，更有人「好言相勸」指她行為病態需要及求醫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popnews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F01.jpg&h=659a608e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉:<a href=\"http://www.popnews.hk/?p=27768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2F%3Fp%3D27768&d=GSdaCmPx%2BB3i8tDtzJQ1YNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6213375d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.popnews.hk/?p=27768</a>"},{"pid":"74aa1d128cd5fd6d51a101b361e1f359c2648437","tid":485834,"uid":37735,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"原本好好地<br />\n<br />\n病態整容"},{"pid":"a77b06889d5fcf66418ca00f3fd8bb27890028a4","tid":485834,"uid":48624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15538185743b28c13fb730d057b515bdc3f32fd2","tid":485834,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c4a19a0ab3d8e5cf3d95081bf8706b5fbcfc00","tid":485834,"uid":26451,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b147c248ca69cde04e798ba4953c12d80f349cfc","tid":485834,"uid":608,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"同班泡菜G一樣<br />\n不過係整容前同整容後個樣調轉返😂"},{"pid":"5ecf4d71bcc6453089d8f4c7a3aa3cc8c9cb4f82","tid":485834,"uid":91096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:17:57.000Z","msg":"似係halloween化裝/面具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0234e701d3ea725f03fab36426187efa3111d72b","tid":485834,"uid":23021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"但真係似WOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14ced75ba1545480d6c35c80cdf7ecbe7f0c4aa","tid":485834,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WTF</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blo